*pcre-light-0.4.0.3 (14 Dec 2014)

  14 Dec 2014; Mark Wright <gienah@gentoo.org> +pcre-light-0.4.0.3.ebuild,
  -pcre-light-0.4.ebuild:
  Bump pcre-light to 0.4.0.3

  25 Jul 2014; Sergei Trofimovich <slyfox@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Drop redundant '<maintainer>' field, leave only '<herd>'.

*pcre-light-0.4.0.2 (02 Jul 2014)

  02 Jul 2014; Mark Wright <gienah@gentoo.org> +pcre-light-0.4.0.2.ebuild:
  Bump pcre-light to 0.4.0.2

  24 Nov 2013; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> pcre-light-0.4-r1.ebuild:
  Stable for x86, wrt bug #488750

  05 Nov 2013; Tony Vroon <chainsaw@gentoo.org> pcre-light-0.4-r1.ebuild:
  Marked stable on AMD64 based on arch testing by Elijah "Armageddon" El
  Lazkani in bug #488750.

*pcre-light-0.4-r1 (19 Oct 2013)

