  21 Jul 2013; Christoph Junghans <ottxor@gentoo.org> pcre-light-0.4.ebuild:
  added ~amd64-linux (tested by me)

  12 Sep 2012; Alexander Vershilov <qnikst@gentoo.org> pcre-light-0.4.ebuild:
