*pcre-light-0.4 (04 Dec 2011)

  04 Dec 2011; Sergei Trofimovich <slyfox@gentoo.org> +metadata.xml,
  +pcre-light-0.4.ebuild:
  Initial version. A small, efficient and portable regex library for Perl 5
